interesting points: The observation lasted for 3 minutes with a single object observed,The object was reported by the master of the SS MORE VICTORY as a giant UFO hovering near the starboard quarter,The observer described the object as potentially descending within an hour,The conclusion from the military source indicated the object was a satellite decay,There were multiple reports of sightings from different perspectives including aircraft and ships during this time.
witness description: The master of the SS MORE VICTORY, a reliable and sincere individual.
